headline: 4 Gas Distribution Stocks Worth Adding in a Flourishing Industry
summary: Rising natural gas export volumes and consistent investment in pipeline infrastructure are strengthening the near-term outlook for the Zacks Utility - Gas Distribution industry. Utilities with stable infrastructure like ATO, UGI, OGS and NWN are well-poised to gain.
